---
title: Cheesy Beef & Slaw Burger with Homemade Beetroot Relish & Zesty Fries
description: When you’re making a burger, you want all the works. A beef patty on top of garlic aioli (also perfect for dipping the fries in) and some fresh slaw is all you need to make a delicious burger, but bring it to the next level with a beetroot relish and a zest of lemon on the fries.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/cheesy-beef-burger-slaw-c5a47b9e.jpg
